This software is provided for educational, research, and informational purposes.
Climate predictions and AI-generated insights should not be used as the sole
basis for critical decisions affecting human health, safety, or welfare.

Always consult with professional meteorologists, climate scientists, and relevant
authorities for important climate-related decisions.

The authors, contributors, and data providers are not responsible for any damages,
losses, or consequences arising from the use of this software or reliance on its
